<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Serpent Newsletter Update</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f5f7fa; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1f2937;">
  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f5f7fa;">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding:24px 12px;">
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; background-color:#ffffff; border-collapse:collapse;">
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td align="center" style="padding:48px 32px; background:linear-gradient(135deg, #1f8a8f, #2db2b7); color:#ffffff;">
                  <div style="display:inline-block; margin-bottom:24px; padding:8px 16px; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.35); border-radius:999px; background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.15); font-size:13px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase;">
                    Major Update
                  </div>

                  <h1 style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:42px; line-height:48px; font-weight:800; color:#ffffff;">
                    Serpent 2.2 is here
                  </h1>

                  <p style="margin:0 0 18px 0; font-size:22px; line-height:32px; color:#ecfeff;">
                    We rewrote the rules (and a bunch of code)
                  </p>

                  <p style="margin:0; font-size:14px; line-height:22px; color:#d7fbfd;">
                    Released: August 2025 &bull; Version 2.2.0
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td style="padding:40px 32px 24px 32px; text-align:center;">
                  <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:20px; line-height:32px; color:#374151;">
                    We've just shipped the biggest update to Serpent ever, and it's a game-changer.
                  </p>

                  <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:20px; line-height:32px; color:#374151;">
                    Seriously. We tore it down. Rebuilt it. Sanded the edges. Polished the snake.
                  </p>

                  <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:20px; line-height:32px; color:#374151;">
                    Now it's faster, smarter, and smoother, like DevOps butter 🧈 on your Salesforce toast.
                  </p>

                  <p style="margin:0; font-size:24px; line-height:34px; font-weight:700; color:#111827;">
                    Let's dive in 🏊&zwj;♂️
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td style="padding:16px 32px 12px 32px;">
                  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse:collapse; background:linear-gradient(135deg, #1f8a8f, #16656a); border:1px solid #1f8a8f; border-radius:10px;">
                    <tbody>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding:28px 28px 12px 28px; color:#ffffff;">
                          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                            <tbody>
                              <tr>
                                <td style="font-size:28px; line-height:34px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff;">
                                  Onboarding That Gets You
                                </td>
                                <td align="right" style="font-size:14px; line-height:20px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff;">
                                  New
                                </td>
                              </tr>
                            </tbody>
                          </table>
                        </td>
                      </tr>

                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding:0 28px 28px 28px; color:#eefcfd;">
                          <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:#eefcfd;">
                            "5-minute setup" isn't just marketing fluff
                          </p>

                          <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:20px; color:#dff7f8; font-size:16px; line-height:28px;">
                            <li>Works with scratch orgs, packaging, or something in between</li>
                            <li>You'll be up and running before your coffee cools down</li>
                            <li>DevOps sherpa guidance included</li>
                            <li>No setup-induced migraines</li>
                          </ul>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td style="padding:12px 32px 12px 32px;">
                  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse:separate; border-spacing:0 20px;">
                    <tbody>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="background:#f8fafc; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:10px; padding:28px;">
                          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                            <tbody>
                              <tr>
                                <td style="font-size:30px; line-height:36px; font-weight:700; color:#111827; padding-bottom:16px;">
                                  A Cleaner, Meaner UI
                                </td>
                                <td align="right" style="font-size:14px; line-height:20px; font-weight:700; color:#4b5563; padding-bottom:16px;">
                                  Design
                                </td>
                              </tr>
                            </tbody>
                          </table>

                          <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:#374151;">
                            We removed the BS. You're welcome.
                          </p>

                          <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:20px; font-size:16px; line-height:28px; color:#374151;">
                            <li>No more 6 tabs doing the same thing</li>
                            <li>No mystery buttons with scary consequences</li>
                            <li>Clean stages, clear steps</li>
                            <li>A UI that actually helps you ship</li>
                          </ul>
                        </td>
                      </tr>

                      <tr>
                        <td style="background:#f8fafc; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:10px; padding:28px;">
                          <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:30px; line-height:36px; font-weight:700; color:#111827;">
                            No Git Setup Needed
                          </p>

                          <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:#374151;">
                            Take that, terminal window.
                          </p>

                          <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:20px; font-size:16px; line-height:28px; color:#374151;">
                            <li>No more wrestling with branches or commit commands</li>
                            <li>You still get the power of Git</li>
                            <li>No praying to the .gitignore gods</li>
                            <li>Deploy, rollback, track, no black belt required</li>
                          </ul>
                        </td>
                      </tr>

                      <tr>
                        <td style="background:#f8fafc; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:10px; padding:28px;">
                          <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:30px; line-height:36px; font-weight:700; color:#111827;">
                            Team-Ready (For Real)
                          </p>

                          <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:#374151;">
                            Add your devs, your testers, your PM, your cat. It's fine.
                          </p>

                          <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:20px; font-size:16px; line-height:28px; color:#374151;">
                            <li>Everyone can stay in the loop</li>
                            <li>Share orgs, track progress, assign tasks</li>
                            <li>No more Slack threads called "Where's the latest sandbox?"</li>
                            <li>Built for real team collaboration</li>
                          </ul>
                        </td>
                      </tr>

                      <tr>
                        <td style="background:#f8fafc; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:10px; padding:28px;">
                          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                            <tbody>
                              <tr>
                                <td style="font-size:30px; line-height:36px; font-weight:700; color:#111827; padding-bottom:16px;">
                                  Supports Org Dev, 1GP, 2GP
                                </td>
                                <td align="right" style="font-size:14px; line-height:20px; font-weight:700; color:#4b5563; padding-bottom:16px;">
                                  Universal
                                </td>
                              </tr>
                            </tbody>
                          </table>

                          <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; color:#374151;">
                            Because you shouldn't have to pick a side.
                          </p>

                          <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:20px; font-size:16px; line-height:28px; color:#374151;">
                            <li>Use any model, all in one workspace</li>
                            <li>Works with packages or direct to prod deployment</li>
                            <li>No config sorcery required</li>
                            <li>Just pick what fits, and go</li>
                          </ul>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td style="padding:12px 32px 32px 32px;">
                  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse:collapse; background:linear-gradient(135deg, #1f8a8f, #2db2b7); border-radius:10px;">
                    <tbody>
                      <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="padding:36px 28px; color:#ffffff;">
                          <h3 style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:30px; line-height:36px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff;">
                            TL;DR?
                          </h3>

                          <p style="margin:0 0 14px 0; font-size:20px; line-height:32px; color:#ecfeff;">
                            If you signed up, poked around, and thought: "Cool idea, not quite there yet"
                          </p>

                          <p style="margin:0 0 14px 0; font-size:24px; line-height:34px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff;">
                            Now is the time to come back.
                          </p>

                          <p style="margin:0 0 14px 0; font-size:20px; line-height:32px; color:#ecfeff;">
                            We built this update for you. For teams stuck between change sets and CLI wizardry.
                          </p>

                          <p style="margin:0 0 24px 0; font-size:20px; line-height:32px; color:#ecfeff;">
                            For every Salesforce dev who's ever yelled, "WHY did it fail this time?!"
                          </p>

                          <table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 24px auto;">
                            <tbody>
                              <tr>
                                <td align="center" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="border-radius:6px;">
                                  <a href="https://serpent.tekunda.com" style="display:inline-block; padding:14px 26px; font-size:16px; line-height:20px; font-weight:700; color:#1f8a8f; text-decoration:none;">
                                    🎁 Check out what's new
                                  </a>
                                </td>
                              </tr>
                            </tbody>
                          </table>

                          <p style="margin:0; padding:16px 18px; font-size:22px; line-height:32px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25); border-radius:8px;">
                            ✨ Let's make your next Salesforce releases actually feel good.
                          </p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td style="padding:32px; border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align:center; background-color:#ffffff;">
                  <h4 style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:18px; line-height:28px; font-weight:700; color:#111827;">
                    Need Help?
                  </h4>

                  <p style="margin:0 0 24px 0; font-size:16px; line-height:28px; color:#374151;">
                    Our support team is ready to help you with the migration and new features.
                  </p>

                  <table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 24px auto;">
                    <tbody>
                      <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="padding:0 6px 12px 6px;">
                          <a href="https://tekunda.com/serpent#contact" style="display:inline-block; padding:12px 18px; background-color:#1f8a8f; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:6px; font-size:14px; font-weight:700;">
                            Contact Sales
                          </a>
                        </td>
                        <td align="center" style="padding:0 6px 12px 6px;">
                          <a href="https://outlook.office.com/book/serpentmeetings@tekunda.com/s/Xfeez_mvmEqNzYIC4kAOIQ2?ismsaljsauthenabled=true" style="display:inline-block; padding:12px 18px; background-color:#ffffff; color:#111827; text-decoration:none; border:1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius:6px; font-size:14px; font-weight:700;">
                            Schedule Demo
                          </a>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>

                  <div style="height:1px; line-height:1px; font-size:1px; background-color:#e5e7eb; margin:24px 0;">&nbsp;</div>

                  <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0; font-size:14px; line-height:22px; color:#6b7280;">
                    Serpent Team &bull; Release Newsletter &bull; August 2025
                  </p>

                  <p style="margin:0; font-size:14px; line-height:22px; color:#6b7280;">
                    You're receiving this because you registered to Serpent.
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
